Name: Cat Dimension
About the game: Cat Dimension - 2D-platformer about cats, made in pixel art. Cat Dimension is an action-packed 2D side-scroller platformer . Blast through this action-adventure hero platformer inspired by classic retro games , and stop an alien animals invasion by teaming up with Willy, our hero. Walk around the colorful 2D world as a cheerful animals who roams it in search of toys and food. You will meet a lot of unusual things, various traps, spikes and hard-to-reach places, but you should not be afraid of them.
